Title: Check user should Register by filling all the required fields
Expected Result:
1. Users should be registered successfully.
2. A successful registration message should show.
3. Mail should send
Steps:
1. Enter valid values in the required fields.
2. Click the Register button.

Title: Check all the optional fields when do not fill data
Expected Result:
1. It should not ask to fill the optional fields
2. User should be registered successfully
Steps:
1. Do not enter any detail in optional fields
2. Enter valid data in required fields
3. Click on the Signup button

Title: Check all the optional fields when filling data
Expected Result:
1. User should be registered successfully
2. A successful registration message should show
3. Mail should send
Steps:
1. Enter valid data in optional fields
2. Enter valid data in required fields
3. Click on the Register button

Title: Check all the valid emails
Expected Result: It should not show any validation
Steps:
1. Enter valid Emails
2. Click on the Register Button.

Title: Phone Number validation
Expected Result: It should show the validation message 8 for Phone Number
Preconditions: Check the phone number when passing alphanumeric data
Steps:
1. Enter alphanumeric data in phone field
2. Click on Register button

Title: Check the phone number when not pass country code
Expected Result: It should show the validation message for country code is required
Steps:
1. Enter valid phone number without country code
2. Click on Register button

Title: Check the phone number when passing country code
Expected Result: It should not show any validation message
Steps:
1. Enter valid phone number with country code
2. Click on Register button

Title: Check the password limit when enter value less than min
Expected Result: It should show validation message
Steps:
1. Enter value which is alphanumeric but less than 8.
2. Click on Register button

Title: Check the password limit when enter value greater than max
Expected Result: It should show validation message
Steps:
1. Enter alphanumeric value but more than 32 (Any Random string with numbers)
2. Click on Register button

Title: Check the password when passing only numbers
Expected Result: It should show validation message
Steps:
1. Enter a value in numbers which is in between 8-32
2. Click on Register button

Title: Check the password when passing valid data
Expected Result: It should not show any validation message
Steps:
1. Enter value in alphanumeric which is in between 8-32
2. Click on Register button

Title: Verify new users should get the welcome email once after the login.
Expected Result: Users should get a welcome email on his/her email id.
Steps:
1. Go to the Email.
2. Enter Login Email.

Title: Verify when passing incorrect Email and correct password
Expected Result: User should not be able to log in and the error message should be displayed.
Steps:
1. Enter incorrect Email.
2. Enter the correct password.
3. Click on the Login Button.

Title: Verify when passing both incorrect Email and password
Expected Result: User should not be able to log in and the error message should be displayed.
Steps:
1. Enter incorrect Email.
2. Enter the correct password.
3. Click on the Login Button

Title: Verify Forgot Password sends a forgot password link.
Expected Result: User should get the forgot password link on his/her email id.
Steps:
1. Click on the Forgot Password link.
2. Enter Email and click on the send button.
3. Now go to mail7.io and enter the email id.

Title: Signup Option for new users
Expected Result: Clicking signup link takes the user to signup page successfully
Steps:
Check whether the signup link for the new user is working
Click Signup link

Title: Verify user should get an error message when he/she enters not registered email id
Expected Result: User should get an error message.
Steps:
1. Click on the Forgot password link.
2. Enter unregistered email id and click on the send button.

Title: Verify user should get an error message when he/she enters the previous password.
Expected Result: User should get an error message.
Steps:
1. Go to the reset password link.
2. Enter the previous password.
3. Click on the Reset Password button.

Title: Verify user should get an error message when password and confirm password not matches
Expected Result: Users should get an error message.
Steps:
1. Go to the reset password link.
2. Enter a different new password and a confirm password.
3. Click on the Reset Password button.

Title: Verify user should able to login with a new password
Expected Result: User should able to login
Steps:
1. Go to the reset password link.
2. Enter a new password and a confirm password.
3. Click on the Reset Password button.
4. Log in by using the new password.

Title: Verify if the user enters a new password that does not cover the basic requirements of password then the user should be displayed error message
Expected Result: Users should get an error message.
Steps:
1. Go to the reset password link.
2. Enter a new password that does not cover the basic requirements.
3. Click on the Reset Password.
